{"id":9738,"date":"2013-11-09T00:00:00","date_gmt":"2013-11-09T00:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/mirandanet.ac.uk\/blog\/2013\/11\/09\/kidsokonline\/"},"modified":"2019-06-29T22:10:53","modified_gmt":"2019-06-29T21:10:53","slug":"kidsokonline","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/mirandanet.ac.uk\/blog\/2013\/11\/09\/kidsokonline\/","title":{"rendered":"KidsOKOnline (KOKO)"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2>Keeping Kids Safe Online<\/h2>\n<p>KidsOKOnline (KOKO) does what it says on the tin! KOKO helps keep kids OK online and provides delightful, safe online learning and social spaces for kids, teens and adults. KOKO loves to help others do the same.\u00a0KidsOKOnline&#8217;s online projects, dedicated to playful social learning, have for 25 years served over 2,000,000 young people and adults in 42 countries &#8211; all in complete safety.<\/p>\n<p>KOKO was founded by Robert and Carole Hart Fletcher.\u00a0They have backgrounds as multi-award winning and pioneering professional educators. They became leaders of Apple Global Education in 1990. They created the Tesco-sponsored SchoolNetGlobal\u00a0with Professor Stephen Heppell in 1998. SchoolNetGlobal\u00a0became the centrepiece of the LearnZone in the Millennium Dome at Greenwich, London.\u00a0In 2001 they created\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.gridclub.com\/\">GridClub Clubs<\/a>\u00a0for the UK Government, which developed into<a href=\"http:\/\/www.superclubsplus.com\/\">\u00a0SuperClubsPLUS<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>KOKO created the Children&#8217;s Community site for <a href=\"http:\/\/www.barnardos.org.uk\/\">Barnardo&#8217;s<\/a>\u00a0with their secure community engine,\u00a0<a title=\"kokokonx\" href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/products\/kokokonx\/\">KOKOkonx<\/a>. KOKO is working with The <a title=\"The Christie\" href=\"http:\/\/www.christie.nhs.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Christie Hospital<\/a>, Manchester on a project to support teenage and young adult cancer survivors. KOKO&#8217;s <a title=\"MySafeTXT\" href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/products\/mysafetxt\/\">MySafeTXT<\/a>\u00a0moderation tools protect the\u00a0<a title=\"IGGY\" href=\"https:\/\/www.iggy.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IGGY<\/a> Community. KOKO acts as expert child safety consultants for the amazing J.K.Rowling&#8217;s <a href=\"http:\/\/www.pottermore.com\/\">Pottermore<\/a>\u00a0social reading site.\u00a0KOKO&#8217;s charity work includes running the\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.kidsandmedia.co.uk\/\">KidsandMedia UK<\/a> website and local community work in the beautiful South Hams of Devon.<\/p>\n<h2>The KidsOKOnline Team<\/h2>\n<p>The Hart Fletchers are joined by world-class expert associates who have worked with government, charities and corporations around the world. They are specialists in online child safety, government online education policy, educational and market research, software design and development.<\/p>\n<p>KOKO is passionate about engaging adults, children and young people and keeping them safe online, and they know exactly how to do it. If you would like KidsOKOnline\u00a0to help you do the same, please <a title=\"Contact\" href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/contact\/\">contact KOKO<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3> KidsOKOnline Team Awards<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-Bafta.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-Bafta.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Awards Bafta - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-Millennium.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-Millennium.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Awards Millennium - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-IWF.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-IWF.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Awards IWF - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-AWards-BETT.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-AWards-BETT.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO AWards BETT - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-Hollis.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Awards-Hollis.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Awards Hollis - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Award-New-Statesman.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Award-New-Statesman.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Award New Statesman - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Award-Guiness.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Award-Guiness.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Award Guiness - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a>\u00a0 \u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Award-IVCA.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/kidsokonline.com\/KOKO\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/KOKO-Award-IVCA.jpg\" alt=\"KOKO Award IVCA - keeping kids safe online\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n","pr